NBA FINALS: PISTONS v SPURS
June 10, 2005
Bruce Bowen
Nazr Mohammed
Glenn Robinson
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







<p>	Q.  Bruce, how are you feeling today?  Working the kinks out? </p>
<p>	Q.  Rip only had six points in the first quarter and then you held him in the last three quarters.  What did you do and what challenges did he present that you were able to counter? </p>
<p>	Q.  Why were you so effective? </p>
<p>	Q.  Do you think he did get shots he wanted to?</p>
